reviewText: It was fun to see the actors out of caricature.i wish I had it a day or two longer because it seemed shorter then the 7 days.
I'm a big fan of this show.  I love seeing cast and crew interviews like these.

Outstanding. If you are a fan of the show then I would watch it if only to hear Ming-Na Wen's personal theory of Skye's true origins and why it would require her to film multiple flashback scenes. : )
